change.subject: Move MediaWikiTestCase::setUp() and tearDown() to annotation hooks
change.commitMessage:
Move MediaWikiTestCase::setUp() and tearDown() to annotation hooks

This removes the requirement that setUp() and tearDown() in the derived
class need to call the parent.

Change-Id: I9d4771c28160356ff58884e3a58fa28c8db4e8a5
